Hi
We are using limelight 2 with the 2020.4 version, and we are trying to create GRIP pipeline.
The GRIP pipeline works fine, which outputs the contours. when I generate the .ll file and upload it to the limelight web interface its successes, and when choosing “GRIP” pipeline instead “Limelight standard” it just refreshes the page.
Anyone who succeeded uploading grip pipeline?

Thanks,
Nir.
